{"/":{"body":"<section id=\"home-wrapper\">\n  <h1 class=\"chars\"><span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">F</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">w</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">k</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">*</span></span></span><br /><span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">2</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">6</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">'</span></span></span></h1>\n  <div class=\"paragraph\">\n    <p class=\"lines\">\n      Lightweight SPA framework for Vite with a single-page entry and simple\n      client-side routing.\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</section>\n","title":"Home","prefetch":true},"/about":{"body":"<section class=\"hero\">\n  <h1 class=\"chars\"><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">A</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">b</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">o</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">u</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">t</span></span> <a href=\"\"><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">t</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">e</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">s</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">t</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">i</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">n</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">g</span></span></a></h1>\n  <p class=\"lines\">\n    A minimal SPA framework built for creative devs who want full control\n    over motion, scroll, and Three.js — without the overhead.\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"intro\">\n  <h2 class=\"chars\"><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">P</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">h</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">i</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">l</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">o</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">s</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">o</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">p</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">h</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">y</span></span></h2>\n  <p class=\"lines\">\n    One RAF loop. One renderer. Sections that know where they live.\n    No wrappers, no virtual DOM, no magic. Just code you can read.\n    The scroll engine is 60 lines. The RAF is 15. The router is 150.\n    Every piece is replaceable.\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"lines\" style=\"margin-top:2rem;\">\n    We believe frameworks should disappear into the project.\n    Not the other way around.\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"stack\">\n  <h2 class=\"chars\"><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">S</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">t</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">a</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">c</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">k</span></span></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Vite + vanilla JS/TS — no build magic you can't explain</li>\n    <li>Three.js WebGPU — one renderer, per-page scenes, shared camera</li>\n    <li>Custom fake-scroll engine — damp frame-rate independent, virtualized sections</li>\n    <li>SSR / SSG via NDJSON streaming — body first, cache second</li>\n    <li>SPA router — clip-path transitions, prefetch, 15s safety valve</li>\n    <li>Loader — tracks images + Three.js textures, numeric progress</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"principles\">\n  <h2 class=\"chars\"><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">P</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">r</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">i</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">n</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">c</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">i</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">p</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">l</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">e</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">s</span></span></h2>\n  <p class=\"lines\" >\n    No abstraction without a reason. No dependency you didn't choose.\n    No lifecycle you can't follow by reading entry-client.js top to bottom.\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"lines\">\n    The scroll engine doesn't know about Three.js.\n    Three.js doesn't know about the router.\n    The router doesn't know about scroll.\n    Each piece does one thing.\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"lines\">\n    When something breaks, you know where to look.\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"footer\">\n  <h2 class=\"chars\"><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">B</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">u</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">i</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">l</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">t</span></span> <span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">i</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">n</span></span> <span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">2</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">0</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">2</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">6</span></span></h2>\n  <p class=\"lines\">\n    No dependencies you didn't ask for.\n    No conventions you can't override.\n    No magic you can't delete.\n  </p>\n  <a href=\"/\">← Home</a>\n</section>\n","title":"About","prefetch":true},"/contact":{"body":"<section class=\"container\">\n  <h1 class=\"chars\"><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">C</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">o</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">n</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">t</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">a</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">c</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">t</span></span></h1>\n  <form data-form=\"contact\" class=\"form\" novalidate>\n<div class=\"form-field\" data-name=\"name\">\n  <label for=\"field-name\">Name</label>\n  <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" id=\"field-name\" required>\n  <span class=\"form-error\" aria-live=\"polite\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"form-field\" data-name=\"email\">\n  <label for=\"field-email\">Email</label>\n  <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" id=\"field-email\" required>\n  <span class=\"form-error\" aria-live=\"polite\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"form-field\" data-name=\"message\">\n  <label for=\"field-message\">Message</label>\n  <textarea name=\"message\" id=\"field-message\" required minlength=\"10\"></textarea>\n  <span class=\"form-error\" aria-live=\"polite\"></span>\n</div>\n<button type=\"submit\" class=\"form-submit\">Send</button>\n<p class=\"form-status\" aria-live=\"polite\"></p>\n</form>\n  <a href=\"/\">Home</a>\n</section>\n","title":"Contact"},"/morphing":{"body":"<h1>Morphing letters</h1>\n\n<svg\n  width=\"200\"\n  height=\"200\"\n  viewBox=\"0 0 200 200\"\n  fill=\"none\"\n  xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"\n>\n  <path\n    d=\"M104.736 57.12C97.056 64.288 83.488 65.568 67.616 65.568V43.04C98.848 42.272 108.064 32.8 110.368 11.552H132.384V188.448H104.736V57.12Z\"\n    id=\"A\"\n    fill=\"black\"\n  />\n</svg>\n","title":"Morphing"},"/slider":{"body":"<section class=\"slider-section\">\n  <div class=\"slider-wrapper\" data-slider>\n    <div class=\"slide\"><span>01</span><small data-pv></small></div>\n    <div class=\"slide\"><span>02</span><small data-pv></small></div>\n    <div class=\"slide\"><span>03</span><small data-pv></small></div>\n    <div class=\"slide\"><span>04</span><small data-pv></small></div>\n    <div class=\"slide\"><span>05</span><small data-pv></small></div>\n    <div class=\"slide\"><span>06</span><small data-pv></small></div>\n    <div class=\"slide\"><span>07</span><small data-pv></small></div>\n    <div class=\"slide\"><span>08</span><small data-pv></small></div>\n    <div class=\"slide\"><span>09</span><small data-pv></small></div>\n    <div class=\"slide\"><span>10</span><small data-pv></small></div>\n    <div class=\"slide\"><span>11</span><small data-pv></small></div>\n    <div class=\"slide\"><span>12</span><small data-pv></small></div>\n    <div class=\"slide\"><span>13</span><small data-pv></small></div>\n    <div class=\"slide\"><span>14</span><small data-pv></small></div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slider-ui\">\n    <button class=\"slider-btn\" data-prev>←</button>\n    <div class=\"slider-progress\">\n      <div class=\"slider-progress-fill\"></div>\n    </div>\n    <button class=\"slider-btn\" data-next>→</button>\n  </div>\n</section>\n","title":"Slider"},"/nike":{"body":"\n<section>\n  <h1 class=\"chars\"><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">N</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">i</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">k</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">e</span></span></h1>\n  <p>2024</p>\n  </section>\n  <section><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542291026-7eec264c27ff?w=2400\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\"></section>\n  <section><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600185365926-3a2ce3cdb9eb?w=2400\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\"></section>\n  <section><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1515955656352-a1fa3ffcd111?w=2400\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\"></section>\n  <section><img src=\"