ef=\"/\">← Back</a>\n  </section>\n","title":"Sony","prefetch":true},"/apple":{"body":"\n<section>\n  <h1 class=\"chars\"><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">A</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">p</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">p</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">l</span></span><span class=\"char\"><span class=\"char-inner\">e</span></span></h1>\n  <p>2022</p>\n  </section>\n  <section><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517336714731-489689fd1ca8?w=2400\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\"></section>\n  <section><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1569770218135-bea267ed7e84?w=2400\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\"></section>\n  <section><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1496181133206-80ce9b88a853?w=2400\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\"></section>\n  <section><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1525547719571-a2d4ac8945e2?w=2400\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\"></section>\n  <section><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512054502232-10a0a035d672?w=2400\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\"></section>\n  <section>\n  <video src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/media/cc0-videos/flower.mp4\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loop muted playsinline controls></video>\n  <a href=\"/\">← Back</a>\n  </section>\n","title":"Apple","prefetch":true}}